Package main.java.matrices

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Matrix
    Interface is the base for all matrix classes and provides access to useful static method functionality.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CMatrix<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
    This GMatrix represents a comparable matrix that contains comparable objects.
    DMatrix
    This CMatrix establishes itself as a comparable matrix using the double generic type, and represents a double matrix.
    GMatrix<T>
    This iterator represents a generic matrix that can contain any object.
